property.name: org.eclipse.equinox.p2.description
property.value:
The Orangevolt XSLT Plugin for Eclipse provides XSLT support to the Eclipse platform.
It is the Eclipse based successor of the java/swing based xmlwrite XSLT editing environment.
It provides many great enhancements when working with xml inside Eclipse. The Orangevolt XSLT Plugin for Eclipse implements XSLT launch configurations, xml editor enhancements, configurable xml outline, an xpath navigator view and many many more.
